reviewText:
Cheap,Ugly. Not because those beads are plastic, but all the material , especially the glass, looks cheap and ugly 
It's cheap price I know, but it just doesn't even worth the price! I purchased another lamp just a few bucks more and looks awesome. 
Not even worth to spend time to return it.
summary: I purchased another lamp just a few bucks more and looks awesome. Not even worth to spend time to return ...
